to add a new paypal button:

1 after first <form> line paste: 
<div id="sizeandcart"><div id="selectsize">

2 after second <table> line paste: 
</div><div id="addtocart2">

3 next to closing <form> paste: 
</div>

4 Replace the 'Sizes' text with:
<span class="selectsizetext">Select Size</span>

5 Get rid of both border="0" parts

6 Replace add to cart image ' src="..." ' with: 
class="addtocartimg" src="img/add-to-cart-button.png"

7 Inside opening select paste
style="width: 91px;"

8 change 'method ="post"' in first line to: 
method = "add"